Interface Scout<O>

Type Parameters:
O - the type of the objects to be updated.
All Superinterfaces:
Remote
All Known Implementing Classes:
BoardScout, ChatScout, ClientRMI, ClientSocket, CommonGoalScout, Network, PlayerScout, SocketHandler
public interface Scout<O> extends Remote
The Scout interface represents a remote interface for updating objects. It is used to notify remote observers about changes in objects.
